overview: Kapri is super stressed but her step-brother Bambino has an amazing massage technique that makes her relax. When Moka Mora realizes it's not her boyfriend who has been massaging her, Domenic Kane is as shocked as she is but he knows she was enjoying it. She can't refuse his proposal of ending what he started. Allie Nicole exaggerates not being able to reach her feet. Her step-brother Jay Smooth gives in and starts massaging her legs, but the tension between them mounts.
title: Be My Massage Therapist
